<view class="page">
  <view class="doc-head">
    <text class="eyebrow">生成处理材料</text>
    <view class="title">理赔、调解、诉讼材料草稿</view>
    <view class="muted copy">这里是核心交付页。所有内容均为辅助生成草稿，正式使用前需要你核对。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card delivery-card">
    <view>
      <view class="delivery-label">当前可生成</view>
      <view class="delivery-value">{{documentDrafts.length}} 类材料 · {{documentDrafts[0].status}}</view>
    </view>
    <button class="secondary-button review-button" bindtap="generate" data-name="起诉状草稿">人工复核</button>
  </view>

  <view
    wx:for="{{documentDrafts}}"
    wx:key="name"
    class="card doc-card"
  >
    <view>
      <view class="doc-name">{{item.name}}</view>
      <view class="muted doc-desc">{{item.use}}</view>
      <view class="material-state">所需材料：{{item.materialStatus}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="doc-side">
      <text class="pill {{item.status === '可生成' ? 'risk-low' : item.status === '需复核' ? 'risk-high' : 'risk-mid'}}">{{item.status}}</text>
      <button class="upload-button" data-name="{{item.name}}" bindtap="generate">
        {{item.action}}
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="warning-panel">
    文书为辅助生成草稿，不构成正式律师意见，不保证协商、调解、诉讼或赔偿结果。
  </view>
</view>
